(101,1,"2019-08-16 01:46:28","2019-08-16 01:46:28","The basic package is the perfect selection for small businesses and people who need a clean, secure, user-friendly, and easy to maintain website that can grow as they grow. It also the perfect solution for those who wish to start a blog!\n\nCreating a well thought out and user-friendly website is paramount to cultivating a rich and profitable customer base.\n\nThe basic package includes the following:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Custom site design up to 5 pages, with 2 rounds of revisions\n<ul>\n 	<li><em>Any additional revisions will be billed at an hourly rate</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n 	<li>Development of Homepage, Functional Contact page/form, About page, Blog page, and 1 additional page.</li>\n 	<li>Migration of site to customers hosting environment</li>\n 	<li>A one hour one on one tutorial/training session to answer questions regarding editing, functionality, in addition to written instructions on how to perform key tasks.</li>\n</ul>\nAdditionally, the following maintenance tools will be installed and configured:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Yoast SEO, to assist with SEO and Google page ranking</li>\n 	<li>Creation of Google Analytics account and integration into the website</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Price: $1000 (USD)</h2>\n<em>This package does not include any e-commerce software or functionality,  content creation, SEO or PPC support or strategy. It also does not include on-going maintenance or troubleshooting.  </em>","Basic","The basic package is the perfect selection for small businesses or people who need a clean, secure, user-friendly, and easy to maintain website.","inherit","closed","closed","","75-autosave-v1","","","2019-08-16 01:46:28","2019-08-16 01:46:28","",75,"http://newportfolio.local.com/75-autosave-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
